---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="App Data Safety - RoyalPrompts" description="Data safety information for RoyalPrompts mobile app - Google Play Store compliance.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">RoyalPrompts Data Safety</h1>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        <strong>Last updated:</strong> December 2024
      </p>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6 mb-8">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-green-700">
              <strong>Data Safety:</strong> RoyalPrompts is designed with privacy-first principles. We collect minimal data and use anonymous login only.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Collection Summary</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-800 mb-3">‚ùå We DON'T Collect</h3>
          <ul class="text-red-700 space-y-2">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Personal information (names, emails)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Location data</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Photos or media files</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Contact lists</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Messages or communications</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Financial information</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Web browsing history</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3">‚úÖ We DO Collect</h3>
          <ul class="text-green-700 space-y-2">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Anonymous device ID (no personal info)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ App version and device type</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Basic usage statistics</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Crash reports (for bug fixes)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ App performance data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Sharing</h2>
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-3">üîí No Data Sharing</h3>
        <p class="text-yellow-700">
          We do not share, sell, or trade your data with third parties. All data is kept anonymous and used only to improve the app.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Encrypted Data Transmission</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">All data is transmitted using industry-standard encryption (HTTPS/TLS).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Anonymous Data Only</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">No personal information is collected or stored. All data is anonymous.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Secure Servers</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Data is stored on secure, encrypted servers with regular security updates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Deletion</h2>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-3">üóëÔ∏è Easy Data Deletion</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-700 mb-3">You can delete your data anytime:</p>
        <ul class="text-blue-700 space-y-1">
          <li>‚Ä¢ Uninstall the app (removes all local data)</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Clear app data in device settings</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Contact us to delete server data</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Permissions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">üì± Device Permissions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">RoyalPrompts requests minimal permissions:</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Internet Access:</strong> To download prompts and sync data</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Storage:</strong> To save your favorites locally</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">üö´ Permissions We DON'T Need</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We don't request access to:</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Camera or microphone</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Location services</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Contact lists</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Phone or SMS</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Calendar or files</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3">üë∂ Safe for Children</h3>
        <p class="text-green-700">
          RoyalPrompts is safe for all ages. We don't collect personal information from anyone, including children under 13. 
          The app can be used by children with parental supervision.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">üîó Limited Third-Party Use</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">We only use essential third-party services:</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Google Play Services:</strong> For app distribution and updates</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>App Store:</strong> For iOS app distribution</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Analytics:</strong> Anonymous usage statistics only</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Questions about data safety? Contact us:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@royalprompts.online<br>
          <strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 48 hours<br>
          <strong>Subject:</strong> Data Safety Inquiry
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6 mt-8">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-green-700">
              <strong>Privacy Promise:</strong> RoyalPrompts is committed to protecting your privacy. We use anonymous login, collect minimal data, and never share your information. Your privacy is our priority.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
